Jerry W. Levin (born 1944), is an American businessman.
Levin is an experienced CEO, turnaround expert and mergers & acquisitions specialist. He is currently chairman and chief executive officer of Wilton Brands Inc., chairman and chief executive officer of JW Levin Partners LLC, and serves on the board of directors of Ecolab (NYSE: ECL); Saks (NYSE: SKS); U.S. Bancorp (NYSE: USB)



